      <title>新兴市场外汇因特朗普、就业数据和美联储讲话而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/emerging-currencies-decline-in-unison-on-prospects-for-trump-2-0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币周二下跌，因为投资者权衡唐纳德·特朗普获胜的潜在影响，优先考虑这些担忧而不是超过预期的美国就业空缺数据和美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的鸽派言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/emerging-currencies-decline-in-unison-on-prospects-for-trump-2-0</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
